{
  "texts": [
    "• CONSOLE outperforms strong baselines on multiple popular VLN benchmarks, including R2R, REVERIE, R4R and RxR.",
    "It also establishes new SOTA results on R2R and R4R in unseen scenarios.",
    "B RELATED WORK B.1 Vision-Language Navigation.In Vision-Language Navigation (VLN), the agent needs to move across complicated visual environments to reach a goal location following human instructions [1], [2], [4].",
    "Therefore, accurate modality alignment is crucial for successful navigation.",
    "Early methods mainly design diverse data augmentation techniques [6], [7], [8], [25], efficient learning mechanisms [9], [10], [11], [26], [27], [28], [29], and useful model architectures [12], [14], [26], [30] for learning useful modality alignment knowledge."
  ]
}